<h1>CashDrop GO - Delete Your Account</h1>
<p class="updated">Account & Data Deletion</p>

<h2>How to Delete Your CashDrop GO Account</h2>

<div class="steps">
<p><strong>Option 1: In-App Deletion</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Open CashDrop GO app</li>
<li>Go to Profile tab</li>
<li>Tap "Delete Account"</li>
<li>Enter your password to confirm</li>
<li>Your account will be permanently deleted</li>
</ul>
</div>

<div class="steps">
<p><strong>Option 2: Email Request</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Send an email to <a href="mailto:cashdropyono@gmail.com">cashdropyono@gmail.com</a></li>
<li>Subject: "Account Deletion Request"</li>
<li>Include your registered email address</li>
<li>Your account will be deleted within 7 business days</li>
</ul>
</div>

<div class="warning">
<h2 style="margin-top:0">What happens when you delete your account?</h2>
<ul>
<li>Your profile and personal information will be <strong>permanently deleted</strong></li>
<li>Your wallet balance will be <strong>forfeited</strong> (please withdraw funds first)</li>
<li>Your dropped banknotes will be anonymized</li>
<li>Your forum posts will be anonymized</li>
<li>This action is <strong>irreversible</strong></li>
</ul>
</div>

<h2>Data That Will Be Deleted</h2>
<ul>
<li>Account credentials (email, password)</li>
<li>Display name and profile picture</li>
<li>Transaction history</li>
<li>Login sessions</li>
<li>Daily challenges progress</li>
<li>Achievement data</li>
</ul>

<h2>Data That Will Be Anonymized</h2>
<ul>
<li>Dropped banknotes (author changed to "Deleted User")</li>
<li>Forum posts and comments (author changed to "Deleted User")</li>
</ul>

<h2>Contact Us</h2>
<p>For questions about data deletion: <a href="mailto:cashdropyono@gmail.com">cashdropyono@gmail.com</a></p>
</body>
